channel.description:
The system cannot find the path specified. Starting CheezScape Server on 0.0.0.0:43594 config\objects.cfg: file not found. Summoning: Loading monsters from Summon.cfg ... Summoning: Loaded 25 monsters from Summon.cfg!
im useing cheez scape

You need to set your paths. Go to the server development/help section and look in alexia’s sticky for a tutorial on setting your paths.[/quote]The error is a misplaced file.
